  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> black rice</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook over a high heat for 30 min or until it's tender (it will still have a slight bite to it when cooked)</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain, return it to the pot and set aside</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and grate the<strong> carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> nigella seeds</strong> and mix to combine &ndash; this is your <strong>carrot salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dice the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> and<strong> cucumber</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Strip the <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely (save some leaves for garnish!)</p>\r\n<p>Chop the<strong> coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>tomato</strong>, <strong>cucumber</strong> and <strong>chopped herbs</strong> in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; this is your <strong>kachumber</strong>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1323.-step-4-x400.jpg",
