            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray with&nbsp;<strong>tin foil</strong>&nbsp;and add the<strong>&nbsp;curry powder</strong></p>\r\n<p>Pat the&nbsp;<strong>haddock bites&nbsp;</strong>dry with&nbsp;kitchen paper&nbsp;and add them to the tray&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Turn the<strong>&nbsp;haddock bites</strong>&nbsp;several times into the curry powder until they're fully coated</p>\r\n<p>Lightly drizzle them with&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong>&nbsp;and put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until cooked through</p>",
